313
00:16:26,780 --> 00:16:27,380
<i>Ban’s Mansion</i>
Anle.

314
00:16:27,380 --> 00:16:29,300
<i>Ban’s Mansion</i>

315
00:16:29,300 --> 00:16:30,700
Anle, why are you here?

316
00:16:31,140 --> 00:16:32,860
