524
00:27:18,460 --> 00:27:19,860
Hua, listen to me.

525
00:27:19,860 --> 00:27:20,620
I didn’t mean that.

526
00:27:20,620 --> 00:27:21,460
I mean, you…

527
00:27:21,820 --> 00:27:23,100
You don’t deserve the Qin.

528
00:27:26,100 --> 00:27:27,780
Hua, I didn’t mean that.

529
00:27:27,940 --> 00:27:29,580
I… Hua. Hua.

