544
00:28:21,300 --> 00:28:24,100
Shi Feixian, what’s your problem?

545
00:28:25,300 --> 00:28:26,660
Let’s talk it through today.

546
00:28:28,660 --> 00:28:30,100
You’ve misunderstood me.

547
00:28:31,100 --> 00:28:32,620
But the soup…

